103-5[6] "Product Information. Zemuron (rocuronium)." Organon, West Orange, NJ.[7] Meyers EF "Partial recovery from pancuronium neuromuscular blockade following hydrocortosone administration." Anesthesiology 46 (1977): 148-50', 1767369485);
