i K, Yoshida H, Shigeno K, et al. "Prolongation of the QT interval and ventricular tachycardia in patients treated with arsenic trioxide for acute promyelocytic leukemia." Ann Intern Med 133 (2000): 881-5[2] "Product Information. Trisenox (arsenic trioxide)" Cephalon Inc, West Chester, PA.', 1767369485);
